sources.description:
Ro-Man, a relentless alien invader, has conquered Earth with his death ray and now hunts the last eight immune survivors hiding in a canyon. He stops their escape ships and becomes obsessed with survivor Alice, defying his own empire's orders to finish his mission. After the survivors fight back, the Great Guidance intervenes with a fiery cosmic blast â€“ but as Johnny awakens from a fever dream, the real Ro-Man emerges, arms raised, charging towards them!
